Subject: [PATCH] dts: qcom: sm8150: nabu: Add panel rotation property

The physical orientation of the panel is portrait, while the
intended default usage is landscape. Add the rotation property
to correct the display orientation in early boot stages like
the framebuffer console.

---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8150-xiaomi-nabu.dts | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8150-xiaomi-nabu.dts
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8150-xiaomi-nabu.dts
@@ -587,6 +587,7 @@
 		vddio-supply = <&vreg_l14a_1p8>;
 		reset-gpios = <&tlmm 6 GPIO_ACTIVE_LOW>;
 		backlight = <&backlight>;
+		rotation = <90>;
 
 		ports {
 			#address-cells = <1>;
